        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Perhaps the anti-royalists thought they could smear the name of Akdilek behind my back and force me into submission.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 4,
        "ActionId": 4,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'But they failed to acknowledge my strength and that I have no intention to become their puppet of a princess.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'That night, when Sophia was brought in front of me. I held my head high and told her the truth.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'She made her choice herself, though it took her some time to do so... To be honest, I was a bit worried she would refuse.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Since asking me to take care of Sophia was Andre\\'s last words. He saw her as a daughter of his own.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Sigh, how dare he ask me, one still hasn\\'t been engaged, to do something like this. I only have experience in raising subordinates, so I guess that will have to do.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'I originally wanted her to become a pawn for me to control, a sword to protect me, but as I watched her grow, I started having other thoughts.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'And perhaps I already had thoughts of helping her \"leave the nest\" long ago.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Perhaps what happened with \"Ashlar\" helped push me in the right direction.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Even though they are skilled in inciting people, I can\\'t comprehend why they think they can hide things from me when their servants are all spies for me.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Well, that\\'s that. Sophia volunteered to become my guard afterward and the rest is history.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'I only want to say that, sending Sophia up to Babylonia is not for a \"trade\" nor is she a \"hostage\". I genuinely hope for this little girl, who has been on this train for her whole life, to be able to experience the world outside.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'I may not be able to apologize to her directly, but I am still responsible for all the blood on her hands. And it\\'s all thanks to these \"necessary sacrifices\" that Akdilek has been enjoying peace since I took over'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'I\\'m really conflicted about her future. On one hand, I want her to become even stronger, but on the other, I want her to enjoy life like a girl her age should. Never mind... It\\'s not something I can decide at the moment.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Jamilah\\'s Letter', 3: 'Forgive me for being selfish and entrusting \"her\" to you. Please train her with care and kindness.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
